= Installation =

To install RubyGems:

<pre>
$ dnf install rubygems
</pre>

= Listing Gems =

To find gems:

<pre>
$ gem search <regular expression>
</pre>

To list installed gems:

<pre>
$ gem list
</pre>

= Installing a Gem =

To install a gem:

<pre>
$ gem install <name>
</pre>

= Removing a Gem =

To remove a gem:

<pre>
$ gem uninstall <name>
</pre>

